      "text": [
        ": سَأَلْتُ أَبَا جَعْفَرٍ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عَنِ اَلْحُرِّ يُلاَعِنُ اَلْمَمْلُوكَةَ قَالَ \"نَعَمْ إِذَا كَانَ مَوْلاَهَا اَلَّذِي زَوَّجَهَا إِيَّاهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4854 - Al-Alaa narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim who said: I asked Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) about a free man performing liʿan (mutual cursing) against a female slave.\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes, if it was her master who married her to him.\""
        ]
      }
    },
